  <entry>
    <title>SSR(ShadowsockR)食用方法</title>
    <url>/2021/07/17/SSR-ShadowsockR-usage/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="介绍"><a href="#介绍" class="headerlink" title="介绍"></a>介绍</h2><p>SSR(ShadowsockR)是一款网络代理软件</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="下载"><a href="#下载" class="headerlink" title="下载"></a>下载</h2><p>官网下载地址：ShadowsockR(<a href="https://github.com/HMBSbige/ShadowsocksR-Windows/releases">https://github.com/HMBSbige/ShadowsocksR-Windows/releases</a>)</p>
<h2 id="软件介绍"><a href="#软件介绍" class="headerlink" title="软件介绍"></a>软件介绍</h2><p>打开软件后，右键任务栏的图标</p>
<h3 id="系统代理"><a href="#系统代理" class="headerlink" title="系统代理"></a>系统代理</h3><table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="center">模式</th>
<th align="left">用途</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td align="center">直连模式</td>
<td align="left">所有应用都没有翻墙的状态。</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">PAC模式</td>
<td align="left">PAC模式是比较常用的SSR会自动识别分流哪些应用需要走代理。（推荐使用，省流量）</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">全局模式</td>
<td align="left">所有应用都都走代理线路，部份情况下如果PAC还是无法打开那么就需要开启全局模式。</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h3 id="规则设置"><a href="#规则设置" class="headerlink" title="规则设置"></a>规则设置</h3><blockquote>
<p>作者也不知道怎么用（有啥用</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="服务器"><a href="#服务器" class="headerlink" title="服务器"></a>服务器</h3><p>你订阅的节点都会在这里显示</p>
<p>连接和修改节点必须在这里点，左键任务栏图标的“编辑服务器”是无效的</p>
<h3 id="订阅-设置"><a href="#订阅-设置" class="headerlink" title="订阅-设置"></a>订阅-设置</h3><p>添加订阅：点击添加</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="center">名称</th>
<th align="left">内容</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td align="center">网址</td>
<td align="left">填你的订阅链接</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center">订阅备注</td>
<td align="left">（顾名思义）</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h3 id="日志"><a href="#日志" class="headerlink" title="日志"></a>日志</h3><p>顾名思义，里面的东西我也看不懂</p>
<h3 id="更多"><a href="#更多" class="headerlink" title="更多"></a>更多</h3><p>一些设置、FAQ和更新</p>
<h3 id="捐赠"><a href="#捐赠" class="headerlink" title="捐赠"></a>捐赠</h3><p>你懂得</p>
]]></content>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>Visual Studio Code配置</title>
    <url>/2021/07/16/Visual-Studio-Code-configuration-C-development-environment/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="介绍"><a href="#介绍" class="headerlink" title="介绍"></a>介绍</h2><p>无…umm…还是扯点什么吧。</p>
<p>在高大上的Visual Studio IDE的影响下，Microsoft推出了轻量级代码编辑器Visual Studio Code。为了好奇心也为了方便学习和工作，本文讲解Visual Studio Code如何配置C++开发环境</p>
<p>信息量较大，请根据目录各取所需。作者巨懒！全文无图！嘿嘿(*^▽^*)</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="下载和安装"><a href="#下载和安装" class="headerlink" title="下载和安装"></a>下载和安装</h2><h3 id="下载Visual-Studio-Code代码编辑器"><a href="#下载Visual-Studio-Code代码编辑器" class="headerlink" title="下载Visual Studio Code代码编辑器"></a>下载Visual Studio Code代码编辑器</h3><p>点击<a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/">这里</a>转到Visual Studio Code官网</p>
<p>下载对应版本的安装包（或压缩包），安装过程略</p>
<h3 id="下载C-编译器"><a href="#下载C-编译器" class="headerlink" title="下载C++编译器"></a>下载C++编译器</h3><p>主流的C++编译器有<code>MinGW</code>和<code>mingw-w64</code>可供选择，推荐使用后者，<a href="http://www.mingw-w64.org/">官网网址</a></p>
<p>点击上方Download按钮</p>
<p>点击Mingw-W64-builds点击Sourceforge跳转到一个国外的网盘</p>
<p>点击Files（上面的步骤太麻烦了？-&gt;<a href="https://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw-w64/files/">便民链接</a>）</p>
<p>滚动条往下拉，可以选择版本</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="left">版本</th>
<th align="left">使用</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td align="left">MinGW-W64 Online Installer</td>
<td align="left">在线安装版，不建议在国内下载，速度贼慢</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">MinGW-W64 GCC-版本号</td>
<td align="left">整合包，为了方便下载，这边直接提供了8.1.0的便民下载链接（快夸我快夸我）</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="center">版本</th>
<th align="center">版本</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td align="center"><a href="https://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw-w64/files/Toolchains%20targetting%20Win64/Personal%20Builds/mingw-builds/8.1.0/threads-posix/sjlj/x86_64-8.1.0-release-posix-sjlj-rt_v6-rev0.7z">x86_64-posix-sjlj(推荐)</a></td>
<td align="center"><a href="https://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw-w64/files/Toolchains%20targetting%20Win64/Personal%20Builds/mingw-builds/8.1.0/threads-posix/seh/x86_64-8.1.0-release-posix-seh-rt_v6-rev0.7z">x86_64-posix-seh</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center"><a href="https://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw-w64/files/Toolchains%20targetting%20Win64/Personal%20Builds/mingw-builds/8.1.0/threads-win32/sjlj/x86_64-8.1.0-release-win32-sjlj-rt_v6-rev0.7z">x86_64-win32-sjlj</a></td>
<td align="center"><a href="https://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw-w64/files/Toolchains%20targetting%20Win64/Personal%20Builds/mingw-builds/8.1.0/threads-win32/seh/x86_64-8.1.0-release-win32-seh-rt_v6-rev0.7z">x86_64-win32-seh</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center"><a href="https://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw-w64/files/Toolchains%20targetting%20Win32/Personal%20Builds/mingw-builds/8.1.0/threads-posix/sjlj/i686-8.1.0-release-posix-sjlj-rt_v6-rev0.7z">i686-posix-sjlj</a></td>
<td align="center"><a href="https://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw-w64/files/Toolchains%20targetting%20Win32/Personal%20Builds/mingw-builds/8.1.0/threads-posix/dwarf/i686-8.1.0-release-posix-dwarf-rt_v6-rev0.7z">i686-posix-dwarf</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="center"><a href="https://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw-w64/files/Toolchains%20targetting%20Win32/Personal%20Builds/mingw-builds/8.1.0/threads-win32/sjlj/i686-8.1.0-release-win32-sjlj-rt_v6-rev0.7z">i686-win32-sjlj</a></td>
<td align="center"><a href="https://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw-w64/files/Toolchains%20targetting%20Win32/Personal%20Builds/mingw-builds/8.1.0/threads-win32/dwarf/i686-8.1.0-release-win32-dwarf-rt_v6-rev0.7z">i686-win32-dwarf</a></td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<p>下好后解压到如下位置（建议，因为我之后都会拿这个举例子）：</p>
<blockquote>
<p><code>C:\Program Files\mingw-w64\</code><br>(为啥是这个路径呢？因为在线安装版的默认位置就是这)</p>
</blockquote>
<p>复制bin文件夹的路径：</p>
<blockquote>
<p><code>C:\Program Files\mingw-w64\x86_64-8.1.0-release-posix-sjlj-rt_v6-rev0\mingw64\bin</code></p>
</blockquote>
<p>回到桌面，右键“计算机”，点击“属性”，点击“高级系统设置”，点击“环境变量”</p>
<p>找到<code>PATH</code>双击，没有就“新建”</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="left">变量名</th>
<th align="left">变量值</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td align="left">PATH</td>
<td align="left">(上面复制的路径)</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<p>然后“确定”-&gt;“确定”-&gt;“确定”</p>
<p>按键盘上的<code>Win+R</code>，输入<code>cmd</code>回车</p>
<p>输入<code>g++</code>回车，如果出现：</p>
<blockquote>
<p>g++: fatal error: no input files<br>compilation terminated.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>则说明配置成功了，输入<code>g++ -v</code>可查看版本信息</p>
<h3 id="下载Java编译器"><a href="#下载Java编译器" class="headerlink" title="下载Java编译器"></a>下载Java编译器</h3><h3 id="下载Python编译器"><a href="#下载Python编译器" class="headerlink" title="下载Python编译器"></a>下载Python编译器</h3><p>请前往官网<a href="https://www.python.org/">官网网址</a></p>
<p>点击Download下方的下载链接Latest: Python 3.X.X(当然这是Python3的)</p>
<h2 id="Visual-Studio-Code-配置"><a href="#Visual-Studio-Code-配置" class="headerlink" title="Visual Studio Code 配置"></a>Visual Studio Code 配置</h2><p>打开一个文件夹，新建一个名为<code>.vscode</code>的文件夹<br>创建两个新文件，及其内容分别为：</p>
<h3 id="扔代码咯"><a href="#扔代码咯" class="headerlink" title="扔代码咯"></a>扔代码咯</h3><p>launch.json</p>
<figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;version&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;0.2.0&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;configurations&quot;</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;name&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;Run C/C++ CMD&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;type&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;cppdbg&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;request&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;launch&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;program&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;$&#123;workspaceFolder&#125;\\$&#123;fileBasenameNoExtension&#125;.exe&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;args&quot;</span>: [],</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;stopAtEntry&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">false</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;cwd&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;$&#123;workspaceFolder&#125;&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;environment&quot;</span>: [],</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;externalConsole&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">true</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;MIMode&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;gdb&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;miDebuggerPath&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;C:\\Program Files\\mingw-w64\\x86_64-8.1.0-release-posix-sjlj-rt_v6-rev0\\mingw64\\bin\\gdb.exe&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;setupCommands&quot;</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">                &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="attr">&quot;description&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;Enable pretty-printing for gdb&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="attr">&quot;text&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;-enable-pretty-printing&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="attr">&quot;ignoreFailures&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            ],</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;preLaunchTask&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;build &amp; run file&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;name&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;Run C/C++&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;type&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;cppdbg&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;request&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;launch&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;program&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;$&#123;workspaceFolder&#125;\\$&#123;fileBasenameNoExtension&#125;.exe&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;args&quot;</span>: [],</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;stopAtEntry&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">false</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;cwd&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;$&#123;workspaceFolder&#125;&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;environment&quot;</span>: [],</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;externalConsole&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">false</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;MIMode&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;gdb&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;miDebuggerPath&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;C:\\Program Files\\mingw-w64\\x86_64-8.1.0-release-posix-sjlj-rt_v6-rev0\\mingw64\\bin\\gdb.exe&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;setupCommands&quot;</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">                &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="attr">&quot;description&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;Enable pretty-printing for gdb&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="attr">&quot;text&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;-enable-pretty-printing&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="attr">&quot;ignoreFailures&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            ],</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;preLaunchTask&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;build &amp; run file&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;name&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;Debug C/C++ CMD&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;type&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;cppdbg&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;request&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;launch&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;program&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;$&#123;workspaceFolder&#125;\\$&#123;fileBasenameNoExtension&#125;.exe&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;args&quot;</span>: [],</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;stopAtEntry&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">false</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;cwd&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;$&#123;workspaceFolder&#125;&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;environment&quot;</span>: [],</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;externalConsole&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">true</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;MIMode&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;gdb&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;miDebuggerPath&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;C:\\Program Files\\mingw-w64\\x86_64-8.1.0-release-posix-sjlj-rt_v6-rev0\\mingw64\\bin\\gdb.exe&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;setupCommands&quot;</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">                &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="attr">&quot;description&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;Enable pretty-printing for gdb&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="attr">&quot;text&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;-enable-pretty-printing&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="attr">&quot;ignoreFailures&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            ],</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;preLaunchTask&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;build &amp; debug file&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;name&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;Debug C/C++&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;type&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;cppdbg&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;request&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;launch&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;program&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;$&#123;workspaceFolder&#125;\\$&#123;fileBasenameNoExtension&#125;.exe&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;args&quot;</span>: [],</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;stopAtEntry&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">false</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;cwd&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;$&#123;workspaceFolder&#125;&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;environment&quot;</span>: [],</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;externalConsole&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">false</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;MIMode&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;gdb&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;miDebuggerPath&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;C:\\Program Files\\mingw-w64\\x86_64-8.1.0-release-posix-sjlj-rt_v6-rev0\\mingw64\\bin\\gdb.exe&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;setupCommands&quot;</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">                &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="attr">&quot;description&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;Enable pretty-printing for gdb&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="attr">&quot;text&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;-enable-pretty-printing&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                    <span class="attr">&quot;ignoreFailures&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            ],</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;preLaunchTask&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;build &amp; debug file&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    ]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>tasks.json</p>
<figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;version&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;2.0.0&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">&quot;tasks&quot;</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;label&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;build &amp; debug file&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;type&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;shell&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;command&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;g++&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;args&quot;</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="string">&quot;-g&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="string">&quot;-o&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="string">&quot;$&#123;fileBasenameNoExtension&#125;&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="string">&quot;$&#123;file&#125;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">            ],</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;group&quot;</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="attr">&quot;kind&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;build&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="attr">&quot;isDefault&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;label&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;build &amp; run file&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;type&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;shell&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;command&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;g++&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;args&quot;</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="string">&quot;-o&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="string">&quot;$&#123;fileBasenameNoExtension&#125;&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="string">&quot;$&#123;file&#125;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">            ],</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">&quot;group&quot;</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="attr">&quot;kind&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;build&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="attr">&quot;isDefault&quot;</span>: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    ]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>保存，重启Visual Studio Code就可以愉快的写代码了</p>
<h3 id="快捷键"><a href="#快捷键" class="headerlink" title="快捷键"></a>快捷键</h3><table>
